Class TransmitException

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Throwable
      • java.lang.Exception
        • com.digi.xbee.api.exceptions.XBeeException

            • com.digi.xbee.api.exceptions.TransmitException
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable

    public class TransmitException
extends CommunicationException
    This exception will be thrown when receiving a transmit status different than XBeeTransmitStatus#SUCCESS after sending an XBee API packet.
    See Also:
    CommunicationException, XBeeTransmitStatus, Serialized Form
